Apex Music v3.20

=What's New=
-Removed some fonts
-Added new default font: apex
-Redesigned the settings page into a grid layout
-Reorganised the intro screen, which now includes a language section
-Added search options in settings
-Added the ability in backup and restore to open the current backup path
-Changed the default filename for backups
-Added volume controls to the now playing theme by a toggleable option
-Changed widgets default album art to round instead of square

=Fixed=
-Misc bugs
-Code optimizations

=Possible Bugs=
-App may crash when opening app through the widgets. This is due to a change by google
-When using the peek now playing theme on tablets or foldables the navigation side rail may disappear completely. this should be automatically fixed when collapsing the miniplayer
